    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Die sabbati qui est tertio decimo die intrante mense ianuarii. Qualiter <rs
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">bonorum virorum</rs> presentia, nomina
                        quorum hic inferius leguntur. <persName><name ref="Iohannes/Bruzabove"
                                >Iohannes Bruzabove</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Formigosa</placeName> obligavit pro <rs>pingnore</rs>
                        <rs key="#Petiae #Wine">petiam unam de vinea</rs>, que est eius <rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietas</rs> et est in <placeName
                            key="#Petiae #Wine">valle de Sablune Ambrosii</placeName>, in manibus
                        domni <persName><name ref="Gherardus  ">Girardi</name></persName>, vice <rs
                            key="#Priors">prioris</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priors" ref="#people/3570">Guilelmi</persName> de <orgName
                            key="#Priors #Missus" ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancto
                            Benedicto</orgName>, tali vero tenore quod hinc ad <rs key="#Markets"
                            >mercatum</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Markets" ref="#places/2418">Gubernuli</placeName> proximum venientem
                        redditos habere debet <rs>XX solidos Mediolanensium denariorum</rs>, quos
                        mutuo ab eo accepit. Si vero in predicto termino non reddiderit predictos XX
                        solidos Mediolanensium denariorum, prefatus Iohannes suprascripto priori vel
                        suo <rs key="#Missus">misso</rs>, proprietas eius vineę et terrę obligate de
                        cetero Sancti Benedicti esse debet, et tertium postea dare debet Iohannes
                        Bruzaboves Sancta Benedicto ut aliquis daret. In millesimo CXXXX, indictione
                        tertia. Isti homines ibi interfuere: <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness #siblingOf"><name
                                ref="Petrus/de Rustico">Petrus</name></persName> de Rustico,
                            <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness #siblingOf"><name
                                ref="Teudaldus">Tetaldaldus</name></persName> eius <rs
                            key="#siblingOf">frater</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness"><name ref="Petrus/Calarius"
                                >Petrus Calarius</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness"><name ref="Martinus/vilicus"
                                >Martinus</name></persName>
                        <rs>vilicus</rs>, qui rogati sunt <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. (SN) Ego
                                <persName><name ref="Albertus/Castellanus/notarius">Albertus
                                Castellanus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> his interfui et rogatus hoc breve <rs
                            key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
